  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project will support the Wales Africa community to increase organisations&#x2019; knowledge and improve practices in project development and delivery, access to funds through grants and share principles of best practice. The project will create opportunities for Wales based organisations and their partners to access training, peer and professional support, resources and tools online. A &#x201C;Case for Solidarity&#x201D; campaign will highlight the work and benefit of international solidarity working.</narrative>
